# Afri Rep Smart Contract Architecture

## Overview
The Afri Rep contract system is designed to create a pan-African reputation layer that bridges traditional trust networks with modern blockchain technology.

## Core Components

### 1. AfriRep.sol
- User profile management
- Skill verification system
- Cross-border reputation scoring
- Vouch-based trust mechanism

### 2. AfriStablecoin.sol
- Pan-African stablecoin (AFD)
- Multi-currency support
- Fiat on/off ramps

### 3. AjoCircle.sol
- Digital rotating savings (Ajo/Esusu)
- Trust-based membership
- Automated payout system

### 4. InnerCircleDAO.sol
- Reputation-based DAOs
- Community governance
- Exclusive feature access

## Security Features
- Upgradeable contracts using OpenZeppelin
- Role-based access control
- Reentrancy protection
- Input validation

## Network Support
- Polygon (Primary - low fees)
- Celo (Mobile-first)
- Local testnets